                <div class ="terms widget">
        <ul>
                        <li class="vothG_lager">
                <a name="vothG_lager"></a>
                <p>
                    <b>
                        <a href="#close" class="hide">
                            [x] click to close
                        </a>
                    </b>
                </p>
                <span class="term">
                    lager.
                </span>
                <span class="definition">
                    German military term for camp or encampment. In the Nazi system these could include transit, labor, concentration, and death camps.
                </span>
            </li>
                        <li class="vothG_folk">
                <a name="vothG_folk"></a>
                <p>
                    <b>
                        <a href="#close" class="hide">
                            [x] click to close
                        </a>
                    </b>
                </p>
                <span class="term">
                    folk-german (Volkdeutsche).
                </span>
                <span class="definition">
                    The Nazi term for ethnic Germans living outside of Germany. The Nazis made every effort to win the support of these German minorities.
                </span>
            </li>
                    </ul>
    </div>
    <ul class="note_popup widget">
            </ul>
